{
  "chapter": 32,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十二回　龙潭虎穴\n\n萧十一郎跟随黑衣人来到宝石山巅，青衣童子和两名轿夫突然被隔空点穴毒杀。黑衣人原来是女扮男装，卖卜瞎子出现与之对峙，二人竟是天宗创始人与第二代主人的恩怨对决。二人突然消失后，萧十一郎以刀劈开亭柱发现地道，进入地下密室。他在石佛腹中发现了逍遥侯哥舒天与黑衣人（冰冰/哥舒冰）的尸体——兄妹二人同归于尽。萧十一郎被困在密室中，后被连城璧带人救出。冰冰的身份和全部阴谋终于揭晓：她利用萧十一郎清除异己，却没想到哥哥还活着。萧十一郎离开后遇见了萧十二郎，收到风四娘留下的诀别信。身无分文的他与船家同行，去恒生钱庄发现自己的巨款只剩一文钱，和一袋花生米。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看看是不是蜡烛燃尽了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快拿根蜡烛点起灯来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_mian_de_jiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "后面的轿夫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这孩子莫非站在那里也能睡着？我去看看。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_mian_de_jiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "前面的轿夫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_mian_de_jiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "前面的轿夫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们两个是怎么回事？难道都睡着了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！好手法，隔空点穴，米粒伤人，像这样的绝代高手，为什么躲着不敢见人？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_tian",
      "speaker_name": "卖卜瞎子",
      "listener": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "text": "我一直在这里，你看不见？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_ge_shu_tian",
      "text": "是你！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_tian",
      "speaker_name": "卖卜瞎子",
      "listener": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "text": "你还认得我？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_ge_shu_tian",
      "text": "你也认得我？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_tian",
      "speaker_name": "卖卜瞎子",
      "listener": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "text": "我若不认得你，谁认得你？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_ge_shu_tian",
      "text": "不错，你若不认得我，谁认得我？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_tian",
      "speaker_name": "卖卜瞎子",
      "listener": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "text": "现在我既已来了，你说应该怎么办？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_ge_shu_tian",
      "text": "是你的，我就该还给你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_tian",
      "speaker_name": "卖卜瞎子",
      "listener": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "text": "莫忘记连你这条命也是我的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_ge_shu_tian",
      "text": "我没有忘，我也不会忘。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_tian",
      "speaker_name": "卖卜瞎子",
      "listener": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "text": "我一手创立了天宗，你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_ge_shu_tian",
      "text": "你怎么知道我在天宗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_tian",
      "speaker_name": "卖卜瞎子",
      "listener": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "text": "除了你之外，还有谁知道天宗的秘密？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_ge_shu_tian",
      "text": "你……你真的一定要我死？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_tian",
      "speaker_name": "卖卜瞎子",
      "listener": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "text": "我已死过一次，这次该轮到你了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_ge_shu_tian",
      "text": "我又何尝不是已死过一次，你又何必逼我……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_tian",
      "speaker_name": "卖卜瞎子",
      "listener": "char_ge_shu_bing",
      "text": "你竟敢暗算我？你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_shu_tian",
      "speaker_name": "卖卜瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫忘记天宗三十六处分堂都是我一手创立的，你还能逃到哪里去？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来你也只不过是块顽石而已，凭什么要我尊敬你？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这世上每个人的生命中都充满了灾祸和不幸，每个人都难免受苦受难，你为什么要例外？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "不知名的人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧十一郎，萧十一郎还活着。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位现在想必已知道，萧十一郎也是被人陷害了，陷害他的人，就是昔年逍遥侯的嫡亲妹妹哥舒冰，也就天宗的第二代主人，在下和萧十一郎之间，虽然恩怨纠缠已久，可是现在都已成为过去，往事不堪回首，放下屠刀，立地成佛，我只希望……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你救了我，我欠你一条命。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又有个萧公子在这里宴客？是哪个萧公子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_er_lang_sui_cong",
      "speaker_name": "船头大汉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "当然就是侠名满天下的萧十二郎。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_er_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十二郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你果然来了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_er_lang",
      "text": "你知道我会来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_er_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十二郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "有个人留了封信在这里，要我转交给你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_er_lang",
      "text": "是什么人留下的信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_er_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十二郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "是个送信的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_er_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十二郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "晚辈本想请萧大侠上来喝杯酒的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_er_lang",
      "text": "你为什么不请？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_er_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十二郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "晚辈不敢请，也不配。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_er_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十二郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "萧大侠，若是没有别的吩咐，晚辈就告辞了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_jia",
      "speaker_name": "船家",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "人家既不想请你喝酒，你站在这里也没有用，还是走吧。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_chuan_jia",
      "text": "该走的，总是要走的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_jia",
      "speaker_name": "船家",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你是不是真的想喝酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_chuan_jia",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_jia",
      "speaker_name": "船家",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你身上有多少银子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_jia",
      "speaker_name": "船家",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "原来你也是个酒鬼，酒鬼本就没有一个不穷的，看来我这趟船又白跑了。你若肯等我半个时辰，再做趟生意，我请你喝酒去。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_chuan_jia",
      "text": "我等你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_jia",
      "speaker_name": "船家",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这条街上的酒都贵得很，我们千万不能进去，可是我每天都要到这里来看看，无论看多久都不要钱的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_chuan_jia",
      "text": "你在这里等一等。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_jia",
      "speaker_name": "船家",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_chuan_jia",
      "text": "我……我进去看看。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_jia",
      "speaker_name": "船家",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "钱庄里可没什么好看的，包子的肉不在折上，银庄里的钱我们也看不见。不管怎么样，能进去看看也不错。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_heng_sheng_qian_zhuang_lao_ban_wei_lu_mian_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "两位有何见教？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 557
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_heng_sheng_qian_zhuang_lao_ban_wei_lu_mian_zhang_gui",
      "text": "我在这里好像还有个账户。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_heng_sheng_qian_zhuang_lao_ban_wei_lu_mian_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "阁下没有记错？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_heng_sheng_qian_zhuang_lao_ban_wei_lu_mian_zhang_gui",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_heng_sheng_qian_zhuang_lao_ban_wei_lu_mian_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "尊姓？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_heng_sheng_qian_zhuang_lao_ban_wei_lu_mian_zhang_gui",
      "text": "姓萧，萧十一郎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_heng_sheng_qian_zhuang_lao_ban_wei_lu_mian_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "原来是萧大爷，不错，萧大爷在敝号当然有账户。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 571
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_heng_sheng_qian_zhuang_lao_ban_wei_lu_mian_zhang_gui",
      "text": "你能不能看看我账上还有多少银子，我想提走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 575
    },
    {
